alliedTelesyn.name: alliedTelesyn
alliedTelesyn.description: Private MIB for ATI next generation layer 2 switches. This MIB contains stacking related groups.

atiswitchEnhStackMode.name: atiswitchEnhStackMode
atiswitchEnhStackMode.description: Enhanced stacking mode of the switch. - Master: You will be able to access the user interface of other switches from this switch and be able to configure the remote switch. Other Masters can also access this switch. - Slave: This switch will not be able to access and configure other switches but Masters can access this switch remotely. - Unavailable: It cannot access any other switches and also no Masters can access this switch. It can only be configured locally.

atiswitchEnhStackDiscover.name: atiswitchEnhStackDiscover
atiswitchEnhStackDiscover.description: Before accessing the enhanced stack, the stack has to be discovered by setting this object to 'discover'. The user is requested to wait for a couple of seconds before accessing the stack as it takes some time for all the remote switches to be identified. Setting the value to 'do-not-discover' has no effect.

atiswitchEnhStackRemoteNumber.name: atiswitchEnhStackRemoteNumber
atiswitchEnhStackRemoteNumber.description: Total number of remote switches detected by the Master. It will also be equal to the number of entries in atiswitchEnhStackTable.

atiswitchEnhStackTable.name: atiswitchEnhStackTable
atiswitchEnhStackTable.description: This table contains the list of all remote switches accessible from a Master switch.

atiswitchEnhStackEntry.name: atiswitchEnhStackEntry
atiswitchEnhStackEntry.description: An entry in the atiswitchEnhStackTable describing the remote switch.

atiswitchEnhStackSwId.name: atiswitchEnhStackSwId
atiswitchEnhStackSwId.description: Entry number of the remote switch in the table. It is also the index into the table.

atiswitchEnhStackSwMacAddr.name: atiswitchEnhStackSwMacAddr
atiswitchEnhStackSwMacAddr.description: MAC address of the remote switch.

atiswitchEnhStackSwMode.name: atiswitchEnhStackSwMode
atiswitchEnhStackSwMode.description: Mode of the remote switch - whether it is a Master or a Slave.

atiswitchEnhStackSwSoftwareVersion.name: atiswitchEnhStackSwSoftwareVersion
atiswitchEnhStackSwSoftwareVersion.description: Software version running in the remote switch.

atiswitchEnhStackSwModel.name: atiswitchEnhStackSwModel
atiswitchEnhStackSwModel.description: Model name of the remote switch.

atiswitchEnhStackConnect.name: atiswitchEnhStackConnect
atiswitchEnhStackConnect.description: Setting this to 'true' will establish a connection with the remote switch. Only one entry in the table can have this value set to 'true' at any point of time. During a remote access, setting its value to 'false' will terminate the remote access.
